videos.headline: Baylor QB Brewer connects with Platt for 22-yard TD
videos.description: QB Charlie Brewer finds a wide-open Chris Platt for a 22-yard Baylor touchdown.

videos.headline: Baylor's Fleeks catches first career TD
videos.description: Baylor QB Charlie Brewer threads the needle and connects with Josh Fleek between two defenders for a 34-yard touchdown to put the Bears up 23-0.
